  "contentHtml": "In this episode Michael and Sarah talk to Mark about the updated Chief Information Security Officer (CISO) Workshop.\n      \n                        <br>\n                        We also discuss Azure Security news about Gateway Load Balancer, Azure Database for MySQL, Confidential Ledger and Trusted Launch. \n      \n                        <br><br>\n      \n                        <!-- Insert episode info from rss.com into NNNNNN and TTTTTT which is the episode number and the title -->\n                        <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/578624?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"The Azure Security Podcast\" frameborder=\"0\"><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/578624/\">CISO Workshop</a></iframe>\n                        \n                        <h5>Links</h5> \n                        <!-- Links to news articles -->\n                        <ul>\n                           <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/578624/'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-pencil\"></i></a></li>\n                           <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-au/blog/gateway-load-balancer-now-generally-available-in-all-regions/\">Gateway Load Balancer now generally available in all regions</a></li>\n                           <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/azure-confidential-computing/azure-confidential-ledger-is-now-generally-available/ba-p/3573336\">Azure confidential ledger is now Generally Available!</a></li>\n                           <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/public-preview-azure-database-for-mysql-flexible-server-data-encryption-with-cmk/\">Public preview: Azure Database for MySQL - Flexible Server data encryption with CMK</a></li>\n                           <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/generally-available-trusted-launch-support-for-dcsv3-and-dcdsv3-series-virtual-machines/\">Generally available: Trusted Launch support for DCsv3 and DCdsv3 series Virtual Machines</a></li>\n                           <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security/ciso-workshop/the-ciso-workshop\">The Chief Information Security Officer (CISO) Workshop Training</a></li>\n                        </ul>"
